    fib4(0) -> 0
    fib4(1) -> 0
    fib4(2) -> 2
    fib4(3) -> 0
    fib4(n) -> fib4(n-1) + fib4(n-2) + fib4(n-3) + fib4(n-4).

    8

    14
    """
canonical_solution:
results = [0, 0, 2, 0]
    if n < 4:
        return results[n]

    for _ in range(4, n + 1):

        results.pop(0)

    return results[-1]
